TYPES:----------------

there are three types of machine learning

1 Supervised learning (has both inputs and ouputs ) : ideal for tasks with labeled data where the desired output is known.

2 unsupervised learning (has only ouputs) : suitable for identifying patterns in unlabeled data without explicit guidance.

3 reinforcement learning :  best for training agents to make decisions through interaction with an environment.


